- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the automation of performance tuning for complex systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with tuning the performance of systems in the cloud. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the implementation of the auto-tuning tool.
